<div>
<h3>FSSAI License</h3>
<h6 style="font-size:18px;">FSSAI Registration is compulsory for small businesses whose turnover is less than Rs. 12 lakhs per year. However any food business exceeding the turnover limit of Rs.12 lakhs per year, then they require a FSSAI License. </h6>

</div><br/>
<div>
